{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857233822,"sessionID":"ses_286aa4a97ffeWBCaySwByZbLyY","part":{"id":"prt_d7956b8fa001AuD4VCVHB1sIl2","messageID":"msg_d795644bd001g01H3sBseQ0Nmc","sessionID":"ses_286aa4a97ffeWBCaySwByZbLyY","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:10","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/plan.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/plan.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心 - Implementation Plan\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: TBD - Implementation plan will be defined during design phase.\n6: \n7: ## Phase 1: Design\n8: \n9: TBD\n10: \n11: ## Phase 2: Implementation\n12: \n13: TBD\n14: \n15: ## Phase 3: Testing\n16: \n17: TBD\n18: \n19: ## Phase 4: Integration\n20: \n21: TBD\n22: \n23: ---\n24: \n25: *Status: Draft*\n\n(End of file - total 25 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心 - Implementation Plan\n\n## Overview\n\nTBD - Implementation plan will be defined during design phase.\n\n## Phase 1: Design\n\nTBD\n\n## Phase 2: Implementation\n\nTBD\n\n## Phase 3: Testing\n\nTBD\n\n## Phase 4: Integration\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/plan.md","time":{"start":1775857233804,"end":1775857233821}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857233824,"sessionID":"ses_286aa4a97ffeWBCaySwByZbLyY","part":{"id":"prt_d7956c8ad001JgR0lve231IcCP","messageID":"msg_d795644bd001g01H3sBseQ0Nmc","sessionID":"ses_286aa4a97ffeWBCaySwByZbLyY","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:11","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心 - Tasks\n2: \n3: ## Open Tasks\n4: \n5: - [ ] Design proxy core architecture\n6: - [ ] Implement HTTP reverse proxy\n7: - [ ] Implement route table management\n8: - [ ] Implement header injection\n9: - [ ] Implement WebSocket support\n10: - [ ] Implement connection pooling\n11: - [ ] Implement timeout and circuit breaker\n12: - [ ] Implement metrics collection\n13: - [ ] Implement access logging\n14: - [ ] Write unit tests\n15: - [ ] Write integration tests\n16: \n17: ## Completed Tasks\n18: \n19: None yet.\n20: \n21: ---\n22: \n23: *Last Updated: Draft*\n\n(End of file - total 23 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心 - Tasks\n\n## Open Tasks\n\n- [ ] Design proxy core architecture\n- [ ] Implement HTTP reverse proxy\n- [ ] Implement route table management\n- [ ] Implement header injection\n- [ ] Implement WebSocket support\n- [ ] Implement connection pooling\n- [ ] Implement timeout and circuit breaker\n- [ ] Implement metrics collection\n- [ ] Implement access logging\n- [ ] Write unit tests\n- [ ] Write integration tests\n\n## Completed Tasks\n\nNone yet.\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775857233809,"end":1775857233823}}}}
